Open the door.

5
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:46,199
You have the keys!

6
00:08:06,729 --> 00:08:10,460
You wanted to go on a trip so badly.
What's wrong now?

7
00:08:10,767 --> 00:08:13,133
You call that a trip?
It was hell.

8
00:08:17,273 --> 00:08:18,968
