Why aren't you picking up?

11
00:10:00,677 --> 00:10:02,406
Are you still angry at me?

12
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:06,578
I'm sorry.
Hurry and pick up.

13
00:10:09,018 --> 00:10:11,418
